gin\": 254, \"end\": 263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Brits\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 389, \"end\": 392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9987508716906955, \"rank\": 0.001246509626254086, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}, {\"begin\": 401, \"end\": 413, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Taylor Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The pair were both trailing behind Laura Lindemann, who clinched gold for Germany in a thrilling spectacle on the Seine.\", \"from\": 415, \"to\": 535, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 450, \"end\": 465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Lindemann\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Laura Lindemann\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Lindemann\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Laura_Lindemann\"}, {\"begin\": 489, \"end\": 496, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"score\": 0.7867882281862512, \"rank\": 0.15003090984840045, \"text\": \"Germany\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Germany\"}, {\"begin\": 529, \"end\": 534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999995192921479, \"rank\": 4.669376436166802e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After a photo-finish analysis, officials judged that Potter had pipped her opponent to second place, awarding Team GB the silver medal and condemning the USA to bronze.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 705, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 647, \"end\": 654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999911241719112, \"rank\": 8.288601168801764e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 691, \"end\": 694, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"score\": 0.9987508716906955, \"rank\": 0.001246509626254086, \"text\": \"USA\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_States\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"However, upon a review later in the day, the decision was reversed with Knibb able to celebrate an improved classification with her team-mates.\", \"from\": 706, \"to\": 849, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 778, \"end\": 783, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.9994153627591861, \"rank\": 0.0005849792416027023, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The saga did not go down well with Pinsent, who took to the X social media platform to complain: \\\"Total balls up by Tri officials to not get the photo finish absolutely right in the first instance.\", \"from\": 851, \"to\": 1048, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"GB bronze correct but there are procedures in loads of sports to learn from that are better than this.\", \"from\": 1049, \"to\": 1151, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1049, \"end\": 1051, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9921917470659563, \"rank\": 0.004732416581580237, \"text\": \"GB\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"As an addition to this - the finish ribbon/tape in tri is necessary and there just for the still photos.\", \"from\": 1153, \"to\": 1258, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In certain circumstances it could block/impede the proper use of PF cameras.\", \"from\": 1259, \"to\": 1335, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Needs to go.\\\"\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The decision was a brutal one for Team GB, who looked to be in control of the race during the final leg before cycling specialist Knibb hunted down Potter ahead of the final transition.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1385, \"end\": 1392, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999911241719112, \"rank\": 8.288601168801764e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1481, \"end\": 1486, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"score\": 0.9994153627591861, \"rank\": 0.0005849792416027023, \"text\": \"Knibb\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Taylor_Knibb\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Brits won gold in this event in Tokyo but will have to settle for bronze in Paris.\", \"from\": 1537, \"to\": 1623, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1537, \"end\": 1546, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"The Brits\", \"types\": [\"Q618779\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Brit_Awards\"}, {\"begin\": 1573, \"end\": 1578, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"score\": 0.9970645013286842, \"rank\": 0.002942386254587652, \"text\": \"Tokyo\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tokyo\"}, {\"begin\": 1617, \"end\": 1622, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996084625, \"rank\": 3.914689456371562e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Discovery+is the new home of the Olympics.\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1669, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The streamer is set to broadcast 3,800 hours of sport live from Paris.\", \"from\": 1670, \"to\": 1740, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1734, \"end\": 1739, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999996084625, \"rank\": 3.914689456371562e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Sports fans can getDiscovery+ for \\u00a33.99a month until the end of 2024 via Amazon Prime's video channels.\", \"from\": 1742, \"to\": 1845, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1815, \"end\": 1827, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"score\": 0.9996782177627437, \"rank\": 0.00032188572432550604, \"text\": \"Amazon Prime\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Amazon_Prime\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This also comes with anAmazon Prime 30-day free trial.\", \"from\": 1846, \"to\": 1900, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Discussing the process, Team GB performance director Mike Cavendish explained: \\\"They want to be able to put something up as soon as they can, and they thought it looked clear, but when you get the photo finish from both sides, it does not look the same way.\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 2159, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1926, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999911241719112, \"rank\": 8.288601168801764e-06, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}, {\"begin\": 1960, \"end\": 1969, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cavendish_banana\", \"score\": 0.605615836241746, \"rank\": 0.6470101000796855, \"text\": \"Cavendish\", \"types\": [\"Q756\", \"Q4886\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cavendish_banana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cavendish_banana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"To be fair to World Triathlon, they went and got me the footage straight away, and as soon as you zoom in you can see it's very, very tight but it is clear.\\\"\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2319, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2176, \"end\": 2191, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.3460132548872874e-20, \"text\": \"World Triathlon\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/World_Triathlon\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Cavendish was then asked about the response of the Team GB athletes to the news.\", \"from\": 2321, \"to\": 2401, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2321, \"end\": 2330, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cavendish_banana\", \"score\": 0.605615836241746, \"rank\": 0.6470101000796855, \"text\": \"Cavendish\", \"types\": [\"Q756\", \"Q4886\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cavendish_banana\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cavendish_banana\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Yeah, of course they are disappointed, they would like to win a silver, not a bronze,\\\" he explained.\", \"from\": 2402, \"to\": 2503, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We use your sign-up to provide content in ways you have consented to and to improve our understanding of you.\", \"from\": 2505, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"This may include adverts from us and 3rd parties based on our understanding.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2691, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"You can unsubscribe at any time.\", \"from\": 2692, \"to\": 2724, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Read ourPrivacy Policy  \\\"But I think that passes pretty quickly when they realise ultimately it's an Olympic medal.\", \"from\": 2725, \"to\": 2840, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"An unbelievable race, it's a fantastic advert for our sport, and that disappointment dissipates pretty quickly.\\\"\", \"from\": 2841, \"to\": 2953, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Pick up your ultimate guide to the Olympics!\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2999, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Going for Gold provides the day-by-day rundown of what's on and when.\", \"from\": 3000, \"to\": 3069, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Clickhereto buy.\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3086, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"SEARCH  CONNECT WITH US  TODAY'S PAPER  See today's front and back pages, download the newspaper, order back issues and use the historic Daily Express newspaper archive.\", \"from\": 3088, \"to\": 3257, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3225, \"end\": 3238, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9606467845904914e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"EXPRESS.CO.UK  Daily Express uses notifications to keep you updated\", \"from\": 3259, \"to\": 3326, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3274, \"end\": 3287, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Daily_Express\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.9606467845904914e-21, \"text\": \"Daily Express\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q11032\", \"Q1092563\"], 